---
title: Herbed Steak & Peppercorn-Mushroom Sauce with Parmesan Potatoes & Nutty Sautéed Greens
description: When the 'steaks' are high... you can’t go past an eye fillet! The accompanying peppercorn sauce and cheesy
potatoes are the perfect companions for this flavoursome beef and with things looking this good, it’s time to set the dinner table, light a candle and pour a glass of your finest beverage. Bon appetit!
